name: Employee Grade List
query:
SELECT
    `tabEmployee`.employee_number as "Employee::120",
    `tabEmployee`.employee_name as "Employee Name::120",
    `tabEmployee`.date_of_joining as "Date Of Joining:Date:120",
    `tabEmployee`.grade as "Grade:Link/Grade:120"
FROM
    `tabEmployee`
WHERE
     `tabEmployee`.status = "Active"
